Living and recording my Diabetes since a few years

Patient name :   ABELMOSCHUS462MOSCHATUS



History : I am currently aged 70 and my doctor also tells me that i have trunkal obesity after having had a visual impression of my abdominal circumference. During the Annual Health check-up in May 2010, HbA1C was 8.6, fasting sugar was 120 and PP sugar 113. The physician advised for testing of HbA1C after three months. After three months in August 2010, the HbA1C level came down to 7.7. Accordingly our physician advised to wait for some more time before starting the medication. On 15th  January 2011, when the blood test was conducted , HbA1C was observed as 8.4 and PP sugar 245.  From 25th January, I started taking medication, Glycomet GP2 (1-0-0), measuring weekly bloodsugar levels both fasting and PP at home using personal Entrus Glycometer and getting done HbA1C test quarterly.The records of the same and the medication prescribed from time to time are presented in the following table.
